metadata.name: SNEEZE GUY #1
metadata.description:
New kind of virus has been detected emerging through out the city. This virus is reported has the ability to mutate, once it find its suitable host. Within 24 hour, there has been a mass outbreak, people panic, the government was obliged to handle public sudden rage.

People who get infected have some kind of symptom stages. It is said that the first symptom will make people sneezing continuously. 5555 peoples got infected.
